{"tid":445684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"心靈上的空虛","createTime":"2017-10-23T14:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T21:00:49.000Z","uid":93947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69446cb399bb9c12b1ec9b021f41f43a995c1bd0","tid":445684,"uid":93947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"一次機緣巧合之下 我遇返一個幾年前識既同事<br />\n傾返計 原來佢已經有男朋友<br />\n約左有一晚食飯⋯⋯唔小心扑左 <br />\n其實事前我地都無預過<br />\n其實我都唔知依家我地係咩關係<br />\n朋友又似再多d<br />\nSP又唔係 我地有傾計個d<br />\nSL...? <br />\n肉體上係滿足 但唔知點解心靈上仲空虛左 <br />\n我都唔知自己叫唔叫沉船<br />\n<br />\n有無人明？"},{"pid":"a7c59ce957c8e3e04527484b0ba4d76ec7067c4c","tid":445684,"uid":102642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"唔好咁上心"},{"pid":"742b65bc3c590b819d8bd2fcb2e1db723b80e8da","tid":445684,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"食個飯就扑咪？"},{"pid":"4b00b9ea01a28b95c25f8c9ec3800eb600ba0670","tid":445684,"uid":72943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">this</span>"},{"pid":"00dc5ad7b20186e52da5c043e44a95e55bc0aa2a","tid":445684,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fe31affc274a0326faa941739367ceea9416152","tid":445684,"uid":11320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:41:57.000Z","msg":"人地有男朋友，你又扑左人，除左一個賤男一個賤西仲有咩身份？"},{"pid":"f69dd1ac646bad2a32d5c22456591758f95c76f9","tid":445684,"uid":93947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:01:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴"},{"pid":"50eb247c240099c233342e0722025baf78711e1b","tid":445684,"uid":93947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T18:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有男朋友，你又扑左人，除左一個賤男一個賤西仲有咩身份？</blockquote